headline: Johnson Controls, FM:Systems energy technologies can provide 155% ROI: Forrester
summary: Enterprises that implement these smart building technologies can reduce energy costs by 10%, chiller maintenance costs by 67% and improve rent premiums by 7%, the consulting group says.
